data.description: Stunning Ranch style Farmhouse on over an ACRE in the heart of Fox Meadows of Caddo Mills. Barnwood LVP flooring welcomes you into this 2020 built home. Farmhouse touches including board & baton Hardi plank siding, barn doors, shiplap, stone fireplace, wood beams, w farmhouse sink! Oversized LR w wood beams and stone fireplace, open flow into the Kitchen. The Kitchen inclds an oversized granite island, stainless steel appliances, granite counters, plenty of cabinet and counter space. Primary bedroom is secluded and includes a walk-in closet with custom shelving. The primary bath boasts a huge walk-in glass shower, dual sinks, granite counters and a stand-alone soaking tub. 2 spacious guest rooms and a secondary bath. Utility room is oversized with designer tile, sink and plenty of counter space. Extended back covered patio is a great spot to enjoy your fenced area, Plus, a 25x35 Workshop! Come enjoy your slice of Texas! NO CITY TAXES, highly rated Caddo Mills ISD!
